om/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-Red0.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEvery single color of the new \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/4hroBJJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003ePhantom Glossy Balm\u003c/a\u003e is wearable and even though Wander is on the lighter side it still shows up on my lips – the pigment is perfect. The regular non shimmer shades are very soft and almost melty feeling once they’re on the lips. The shimmer version is smooth without texture but they have a slightly stiffer feel which I actually like better.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSince these are glossy balms lasting power isn’t going to be long, but they don’t slide off easily and I really like that the finish is forgiving so it fades nicely. They are nicely hydrating and smooth without feeling thick.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Hourglass team sent a beautiful press box with the new shades and also included three from the permanent lineup. I’ve reviewed them \u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2023/07/new-launches-from-hourglass.html\" rel=\"\"\u003e\u003cem\u003ehere\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2024/02/new-hourglass-lip-launches-2024.html\" rel=\"\"\u003e\u003cem\u003ehere\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2022/10/hourglass-ambient-lighting-edit-unlocked-holiday-2022.html\" rel=\"\"\u003e\u003cem\u003ehere\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e but thought I’d add them here too including \u003cspan\u003eDesire\u003c/span\u003e (rose mauve), \u003cspan\u003eLure\u003c/span\u003e (plum) and \u003cspan\u003eSense\u003c/span\u003e (the best nude pink).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"Hourglass Phantom Volumizing Glossy Lip Balm swatches\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"Hourglass Phantom Volumizing Glossy Lip Balm – New Shades for Spring 2025.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2025/02/hourglass-phantom-volumizing-glossy-lip-balm-new-shades.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Hourglass Phantom Volumizing Glossy Lip Balm – New Shades\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Glossy-Balm-swatches-BEAUTYLOOKBOOK.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Volumizing-Glossy-Balm-Desire-Lure-Sense.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Hourglass-Phantom-Volumizing-Glossy-Balm-Desire-Lure-Sense-1440x2364.jpg\" 